org.jfree.data.time

Class Hour

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jfree.data.time.RegularTimePeriod
      • org.jfree.data.time.Hour
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable, TimePeriod, org.jfree.date.MonthConstants

    public class Hour
extends RegularTimePeriod
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents an hour in a specific day.

    This class is immutable, which is a requirement for all RegularTimePeriod subclasses.

    See Also:
    Serialized Form

        public static Hour parseHour(java.lang.String s)
